{
  "schema_version": 2,
  "notes": [
    "Populate this file with project-specific checks and reviewer commands before using reviewer gates.",
    "Commands may be strings or argv arrays. Supported placeholders: {project_root}, {packet_path}, {prompt_path}, {prompt}.",
    "Reviewer gates fail hard by default when required reviewers are not configured or unavailable.",
    "Legacy projects may still use a top-level checks list. allox treats that legacy list as both milestone and final gate checks unless gate-specific checks are defined."
  ],
